Definition: a highly poisonous gas or volatile liquid that smells like bitter almonds
Example: becomes a gas at around 90 degree Fahrenheit and is most dangerous when inhaled; the anhydride of hydrocyanic acid; used in manufacturing
Synonyms: compound, a, highly, poisonous, gas, or, volatile, liquid, that, smells, like, bitter, almonds, becomes, at, around, degree, Fahrenheit, and, is, most, dangerous, when, inhaled, the, anhydride, of, hydrocyanic, acid, used, in, manufacturing
Category: noun.substance
